quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,50,"Yamiroore Amen wonaali, si wanaa [konngol] gootol pet, [yaawira] wa hin∆īaango yiitere"
  54,51,Gom…óii Men halkiino yeradii…ďe mon. Hara wooday waajitoray…óo
  54,52,Kala huunde nde …ďe golli no ka nder …óeri
  54,53,"kala kadi toksum e mawnukum, ko winndaa…óum"
  54,54,"Pellet, gom…óu…ďe …ďen wonii e Aljannaaji e can…ói"
  54,55,"e toolorde goonga, ka Laam…óo Hattan…óo"
  55,1,Jom HinaraŇčke On
  55,2,O anndinii Alqur'aana
  55,3,O tagi ne…ó…óaŇčke
  55,4,O anndini mo …ďanngingol
  55,5,"Naange ngen e lewru ndun [hino dogira] limoore"
  55,6,"koode …óen kadi e le…ó…óe …óen, hino sujjude"
  55,7,"Kammu ngun, O toownu ngu. O wa…ói nun…óal ngal"
  55,8,fii wata on bewu ka peesir…óe
  55,9,√Ďinniron etugol ngol no nun…óiri. Wata on …óuytu peesir…óe …óen
  55,10,"Leydi ndin, O wa…óanndi tagoore nden"
  55,11,"muuyantee…ói hino e mayri, e le…ó…óe tamaro mar…óe po∆ī∆īi"
  55,12,"e gabbe mar…óe √Īaande, e uurngol"
  55,13,E ko hon…ói e neemaaji Joomi mon …óin woni ko fennoton
  55,14,"O tagiri ne…ó…óo on immorde e loopal, wa'ungal wa ko ju…óaa"
  55,15,"O tagiri jinnaaji …óin, immorde e lew lewndu yiite laa…ďuki"
  55,16,E ko hon…ói e neemaaji Joomi mon …óin yeddoton
